				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><table class="metadata plainlinks ambox ambox-move" style="">
<tr>
<td class="mbox-image">
<div style="width: 52px;"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0f/Mergefrom.svg/50px-Mergefrom.svg.png" width="50" height="20" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0f/Mergefrom.svg/75px-Mergefrom.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0f/Mergefrom.svg/100px-Mergefrom.svg.png 2x" /></div>
</td>
<td class="mbox-text" style=""><span class="mbox-text-span">It has been suggested that <i><a href="Spam_in_blogs" title="Spam in blogs">spam in blogs</a></i> be <a href="Wikipedia_Merging" title="Wikipedia:Merging">merged</a> into this article or section. (<a href="Talk_Spam_(electronic)" title="Talk:Spam (electronic)">Discuss</a>) <small><i>Proposed since October 2012.</i></small> </span></td>
